I’m Kitty. I’m a transfeminine web engineer and engineering leader based in Berlin, with nearly 15
years of experience, currently focused on engineering excellence, accessibility, diversity and
inclusion. In recent years, I have led engineering teams at [N26](https://n26.com),
[Gorillas](<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gorillas_(company)>), [cofenster](https://cofenster.com/),
and [Scilife](https://scilife.io) — all companies I helped grow and scale.

